behavior slice_bread(bread: item, cutting_board: item, knife: item):

        assert grabbable(bread)
        assert grabbable(knife)
        assert cuttable(bread)
        achieve_once inhand(knife)
        achieve on(bread, cutting_board)
        achieve cut(bread)

behavior move_to_toaster_with_bread(bread:item, toaster:item):
    body:
        achieve_once inhand(bread)
        # Hold the bread temporarily to move towards the toaster
        achieve close_char(char, toaster)
        # Move the character close to the toaster

behavior place_bread_in_toaster(bread:item, toaster:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(bread, toaster)
        # Put the bread inside the toaster for toasting

behavior start_toasting(toaster:item):
    body:
        achieve plugged(toaster)
        # Ensure the toaster is plugged in
        achieve is_on(toaster)
        # Turn the toaster on to start toasting

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind bread: item where:
            is_food_bread(bread) and cut(bread) 
            # Ensure the bread is already cut

        bind toaster: item where:
            is_toaster(toaster)

        move_to_toaster_with_bread(bread, toaster)
        place_bread_in_toaster(bread, toaster)
        start_toasting(toaster)
